PrecisAmendment to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (COLLECTION OF PREMIUMS) REGULATIONS establishing the tables of premiums for the year 1992, whereby employers will be able to determine the amount of unemployment insurance premiums deductible from their employees' remuneration paid in 1992 in respect of the pay periods provided for in those tables.

precis:
Amendment to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (COLLECTION OF PREMIUMS)
REGULATIONS establishing the tables of premiums for the year 1992, whereby
employers will be able to determine the amount of unemployment insurance
premiums deductible from their employees' remuneration paid in 1992 in
respect of the pay periods provided for in those tables.
